// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-3136 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 8c607264-3109-5557-8720-a779bf690c6f

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
